text: At the next BitcoinNYC Meetup I'm going to be talking about self-sovereign identity, GDPR, #RebootingWebOfTrust design shops (April 21st in Paris, September in Boston?), and try to have a more philosophical conversations about consent vs coercion, power resistance, privacy vs accountability, & fungibility ~≠ anonymity. <https://www.meetup.com/BitcoinNYC/events/236706902/>
